NewsArticle.Article:
&lt;p&gt;We did a lot of a work behind the scenes to create a faster system, and developed a lot of new features requested by the community, to make your NEXSO experience that much better.  Here is a look at a few of the new features you now have access to as part of our community:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;New Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Change solution cover photos&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Solution pages now feature a large full-width cover photo that can be switched by the owner at any time simply by selecting &amp;ldquo;Change cover photo&amp;rdquo; in the top-left of the image. These images are a simple way to improve the instant appeal of a solution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/7/Blog/change-banner.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Send private messages&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Registered users now have the ability to communicate directly with solution owners through solution pages. Look for the &amp;ldquo;Send a message&amp;rdquo; button. All conversations can be accessed through a new &amp;ldquo;Messages&amp;rdquo; section, making it easier to collaborate with colleagues and make new connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/7/Blog/MyMessages.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;New feedback tool&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A new feedback section at the base of solution pages makes interacting with solutions a much more satisfying experience for the whole community. The addition of new social share tools also provide new opportunities for increasing solution visibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/7/Blog/feedback.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;New blog section&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We often hear truly inspiring and fascinating stories from our community, so we decided we need a place to start sharing them. The NEXSO blog will continue to be built out as we gather more of your success stories and look for ways to help you improve your solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/7/Blog/blog.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Display improvements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Better mobile experience
&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With more users now visiting NEXSO on a mobile device we understand the importance of delivering an exceptional mobile experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Improved solution layout
&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All solution tags have been relocated to an &amp;ldquo;Overview&amp;rdquo; section at the top right of the page to improve readability and to provide a short snapshot of the solution. With a greater focus on the main content it becomes even more important that each section is well written. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;More modern look and feel
&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lastly, perhaps the most noticeable change is our new homepage, and a more modern look and feel that reaches across many of the pages you frequently visit on NEXSO.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We hope you enjoy using these new features, that they help you to improve how your solution is presented on NEXSO, and also help to provide some increased visibility for your work. &lt;/p&gt;

