&lt;p&gt;NEXSO is an online community where innovators, social and business entrepreneurs, organizations, donors, and investors come together to promote and spread solutions that are improving the quality of life of people living in Latin America &amp;amp; the Caribbean. NEXSO is an initiative of the MIF, a member of the Inter American Development Bank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Daily, thousands of people and organizations creatively conceive solutions for their communities and localities. If you are one of them, and are passionate about solving social, economic, environmental issues, then NEXSO is the right place for you. NEXSO is a community that hosts and strengthens multiple different types of solutions, while at the same time it is a platform that provides solutions for those who are seeking one.
NEXSO was created so you can easily learn about new opportunities available, as well as interact, exchange knowledge, and connect. Now you have a direct channel to communicate with people that are also making change happen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We know you have great solutions and you want to share them. Together we can transform a good idea into an impactful solution or increase the impact of an existing solution by replicating it in other areas or countries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It all starts when you share your solution! Now NEXSO brings us together.&lt;/p&gt;
